The paper also proposes a neural network-based approach, which falls under the cs.MM (Multimedia) category. The paper uses deep learning techniques, which are often associated with the cs.LG (Machine Learning) category. Additionally, the paper involves the use of heuristics and optimization techniques, which are associated with the cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) category. Finally, the paper involves the analysis of datasets and performance evaluation, which are associated with the cs.GR (Graphics) category.
